data.description: Welcome to the perfect combination of home and yard! Situated on a half acre lot in Genoa Twp, Hartland Schools, this spacious 4-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom ranch offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. With 2,300 square feet of finished living space, there's plenty of room for everyone to spread out and relax. The open-concept main floor features gleaming hardwood floors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen provides ample counter space, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast nook that's perfect for casual dining. The living room is large and airy with natural light along with all 3 main level bedrooms, providing plenty of space and privacy! The finished lower level provides additional living space with a family room, additional bedroom and flex area. The half-acre lot provides plenty of room for outdoor activities paired with the screened-in porch, you'll love spending all day overlooking your yard! Close to Downtown Brighton, Hartland and Howell, this Home is situated in the ideal location for accessibility to schools, parks, restaurants, shops, freeways and more!
